---
interface Props {
  theme?: 'studio' | 'night';
}
const { theme = 'studio' } = Astro.props;
const night = theme === 'night';
---
<footer
  class:list={[
    night ? 'bg-[#070F11] text-night-ink border-t border-[color:var(--night-line)]' : 'bg-ink text-paper',
  ]}
  data-theme="night"
>
  <div class="wrap pt-14 pb-8">
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1.6fr_1fr_1fr_1fr]">
      <div>
        <p class="font-display font-semibold text-[1.2rem] flex items-baseline gap-2">
          Studio Fisiatrico Russo
          <span class:list={['w-2 h-2 rounded-full shrink-0', night ? 'bg-aqua' : 'bg-accent']} aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-[32ch] text-[0.92rem] opacity-70">
          Fisiatria, riabilitazione ed esercizio terapeutico: un solo percorso, dalla diagnosi al ritorno al movimento.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[0.85rem] opacity-70">
          Dott. Antonino Russo, Medico Chirurgo<br />Specialista in Medicina Fisica e Riabilitativa
        </p>
        <!-- TODO cliente: n. iscrizione OMCeO Catania da aggiungere qui -->
      </div>
      <nav aria-label="Sezioni Studio">
        <h3 class="font-body font-bold text-[0.74rem] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-3.5">Studio</h3>
        <ul class="list-none m-0 p-0 flex flex-col gap-2 text-[0.92rem]">
          <li><a class="inline-block py-1 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-aqua transition" href="/#percorso">Il percorso</a></li>
          <li><a class="inline-block py-1 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-aqua transition" href="/#trattamenti">Cosa trattiamo</a></li>
          <li><a class="inline-block py-1 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-aqua transition" href="/#faq">FAQ</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <nav aria-label="Sezioni Motion">
        <h3 class="font-body font-bold text-[0.74rem] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-3.5">Motion</h3>
        <ul class="list-none m-0 p-0 flex flex-col gap-2 text-[0.92rem]">
          <li><a class="inline-block py-1 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-aqua transition" href="/motion/">I programmi</a></li>
          <li><a class="inline-block py-1 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-aqua transition" href="/motion/#metodo">Il metodo</a></li>
          <li><a class="inline-block py-1 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-aqua transition" href="/motion/#coach">Il coach</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <nav aria-label="Contatti">
        <h3 class="font-body font-bold text-[0.74rem] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase mb-3.5">Contatti</h3>
        <ul class="list-none m-0 p-0 flex flex-col gap-2 text-[0.92rem]">
          <li><a class="inline-block py-1 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-aqua transition" href="/#prenota">Prenota</a></li>
          <li><a class="inline-block py-1 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-aqua transition" href="tel:+393421904804">+39 342 190 4804</a></li>
          <li><a class="inline-block py-1 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-aqua transition" href="mailto:antoninorusso994@gmail.com">antoninorusso994@gmail.com</a></li>
          <li><a class="inline-block py-1 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-aqua transition" href="https://www.instagram.com/toni__russo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a></li>
          <li><a class="inline-block py-1 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-aqua transition" href="https://www.miodottore.it/antonino-russo-4/fisiatra/catania" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MioDottore</a></li>
          <li><a class="inline-block py-1 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 hover:text-aqua transition" href="/privacy/">Privacy</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 pt-5 border-t border-white/15 flex flex-wrap justify-between gap-3 text-[0.8rem] opacity-60">
      <span>© 2026 Studio Fisiatrico Russo · Misterbianco (Catania)</span>
      <span>P.IVA 06111760879</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
